wiki.summary: "Call On Me" is a single released by RAYE on July 11, 2021, and was the last song released while under contract with Polydor Records. The song was written for her sister who was going through a difficult time. It was intended to be the lead single for RAYE’s debut album, However Raye was Dropped from Polydor Records. But it was only The beginning for RAYE as in 2022, she would release "Escapism." and it would be the Breakout Song for her, gaining popularity worldwide. Read more on Last.fm.
